Makanan? Aku tak bisa cium apa pun.

326
00:28:25,829 --> 00:28:27,372
Toddy panas.

327
00:28:27,455 --> 00:28:29,207
Membantu melegakan sinus.

328
00:28:32,460 --> 00:28:33,503
Terima kasih.

329
00:28:33,586 --> 00:28:35,672
Kau harus terus minum ini.

330
