Aku ingin kau tahu,
menurutku kau pahlawan.

346
00:29:46,701 --> 00:29:49,329
Bersembunyi di sini, mengasihani diri.

347
00:29:50,163 --> 00:29:51,831
Di belakang,

348
00:29:51,915 --> 00:29:55,460
