Hei! Lepaskan dia!
Apa yang kau lakukan? Ayah!

425
00:40:13,160 --> 00:40:14,829
Ayah! Hei!

426
00:40:35,641 --> 00:40:38,853
Tolong! Lepaskan! Tolong!

427
00:40:39,937 --> 00:40:41,647
Astaga! Ayah...

428
00:40:51,282 --> 00:40:53,159
Bertahanlah. Kita ke rumah sakit.

429
00:41:12,386 --> 00:41:13,596
Ayo!

430
00:41:15,347 --> 00:41:17,975
Hei, Berengsek, ini bukan urusanmu.

431
00:41:19,435 --> 00:41:20,436
Ayo.

432
00:41:48,088 --> 00:41:49,924
Kita harus bunuh bedebah ini.

433
00:41:50,007 --> 00:41:51,759
Tidak. Biarkan saja.

434
00:41:55,971 --> 00:41:56,972
Tunggu.

435
00:42:09,443 --> 00:42:10,569
Tuhan ampuni aku.

436
00:42:14,949 --> 00:42:16,867
Biarkan dia. Mari kita pergi.

437
00:42:49,066 --> 00:42:52,570
Kita sungguh kehabisan kalkun?
Kau tak mampir ke deli?

438
00:42:53,279 --> 00:42:55,030
Aku mampir.

439
00:42:55,114 --> 00:42:59,034
Ada masalah pembayaran di kasir.

440
00:43:00,244 --> 00:43:03,497
Aku ingin pesta selesai
sebelum membahasnya.

441
